snippet.title: Brutal Orchestra Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Out now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1734320/Brutal_Orchestra/
Join us on Discord: https://discord.gg/b6Gm7ctKcX
Follow us on Itch: https://itsthemaceo.itch.io/
Follow Brutal Orchestra on Twitter: https://twitter.com/ItsTheMaceo

Hieronymus Bosch's Brutal Orchestra is a Turn-Based Roguelike Strategy game with resource management and deck-building elements. Employ the help of damaged and daring fools, equip ancient and insidious items and make deals with the devil on your path to revenge.
